{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a customizable Shopify section with a horizontal split layout (50/50).
    Requirements:
    The section should have two equal halves (left and right).
    Each half must have its own background color (editable in settings).
    Each half should contain editable text (headline).
    Text should be centered vertically and horizontally.
    Allow customization for:
    Left text content
    Right text content
    Left background color
    Right background color
    Text color for both sides
    Font size and font weight
    Make the section responsive (stack vertically on mobile).
    Add optional spacing (padding top/bottom).
    Use clean, modern styling similar to Shopify Dawn theme.
    Default example:
    Left side: "BUY 2 GET 1 FREE"
    Right side: "BUNDLE WITH A BESTSELLER"
    Ensure the section is easy to reuse and customizable from the Shopify theme editor., Create a Shopify section with a 50/50 split layout that looks clean on both desktop and mobile.
    
    Requirements:
    
    Layout:
    
    * Two equal columns (left and right) on desktop (50% width each).
    * On mobile, stack the sections vertically (one on top of the other).
    * Each block must always have equal height on desktop.
    
    Styling:
    
    * Each side has its own editable background color.
    * Text must be perfectly centered (both vertically and horizontally).
    * Use flexbox for alignment (not absolute positioning).
    * Add consistent padding (e.g. 20px–40px).
    
    Text:
    
    * Editable text for left and right side.
    * Allow control for:
    
      * Font size (desktop + mobile separately)
      * Font weight
      * Text color
    
    Mobile optimization (VERY IMPORTANT):
    
    * Ensure no extra spacing or uneven heights.
    * Make both stacked sections look like clean banners.
    * Reduce font size slightly on mobile.
    * Keep text centered and visually balanced.
    
    Optional:
    
    * Add a subtle divider line between sections (desktop only).
    * Add hover effect (slight brightness change).
    
    Default content:
    
    * Left: "BUY 2 GET 1 FREE"
    * Right: "BUNDLE WITH A BESTSELLER"
    
    Important:
    
    * The section must look like a clean promotional banner, not like two separate boxes.
    * Avoid large empty gaps or misalignment on mobile.
    , Make the section much more compact.
    
    * Remove all extra spacing, margins and gaps.
    * Reduce padding to around 10–15px.
    * Set a smaller fixed height (around 50–70px).
    * Ensure there is NO space between the two halves.
    * Make it look like a slim announcement bar, not large boxes.
    
    Mobile:
    
    * Reduce height even more on mobile (around 40–60px).
    * Reduce font size slightly.
    * Remove any spacing between stacked sections.
    
    Important:
    
    * The layout should feel tight, clean, and minimal.
    * No large empty areas.
    , Adjust the text alignment to reduce the visual gap between the two texts.
    
    * Keep the 50/50 layout.
    * Move the left text slightly to the right (towards center).
    * Move the right text slightly to the left (towards center).
    * Do NOT fully center text inside each half.
    * Instead, align text closer to the middle divider.
    
    Spacing:
    
    * Add a small horizontal offset (e.g. padding or transform).
    * Keep the overall layout balanced.
    
    Important:
    
    * The two texts should feel visually closer together.
    * The middle gap should be tight, like a continuous banner.
    , Update this section so the left and right panels are controlled independently in the theme editor.
    
    Add separate settings for:
    
    * Left text
    * Right text
    * Left text color
    * Right text color
    * Left background color
    * Right background color
    * Left font size
    * Right font size
    * Left font weight
    * Right font weight
    * Left text alignment/offset
    * Right text alignment/offset
    
    Keep the section compact, responsive, and with reduced visual gap between the texts.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-promo-split-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-promo-split__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    {% if block.settings.show_divider %}
      gap: 1px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
    {% else %}
      gap: 0;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-promo-split__panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_desktop }}px;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.min_height_desktop }}px;
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-promo-split__panel--left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.left_bg_color }};
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-right: {{ block.settings.left_text_offset }}px;
  }

  .ai-promo-split__panel--right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.right_bg_color }};
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding-left: {{ block.settings.right_text_offset }}px;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover %}
    .ai-promo-split__panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.1);
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-promo-split__text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.letter_spacing }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.text_transform }};
    max-width: 100%;
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .ai-promo-split__text--left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.left_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.left_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.left_font_weight }};
  }

  .ai-promo-split__text--right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.right_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.right_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.right_font_weight }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-promo-split__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .ai-promo-split__panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.padding_mobile }}px;
      min-height: {{ block.settings.min_height_mobile }}px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .ai-promo-split__panel--left-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-promo-split__panel--right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-left: {{ block.settings.padding_mobile }}px;
      padding-right: {{ block.settings.padding_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-promo-split__text--left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.left_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-promo-split__text--right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.right_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<promo-split-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-promo-split-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-promo-split__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-promo-split__panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-promo-split__panel--left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.left_text != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-promo-split__text-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-promo-split__text--left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.left_text }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="ai-promo-split__panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-promo-split__panel--right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.right_text != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-promo-split__text-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-promo-split__text--right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.right_text }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</promo-split-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class PromoSplit{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }
    }
    customElements.define('promo-split-{{ ai_gen_id }}', PromoSplit{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

